none.description:
{Mind Whip}

Lashes the target's psyche with raw magical force. Deals damage to all living creatures and Golems, bypassing magic resistances. Has no effect on Undead, Elementals, or Siege Engines.

Unit takes (Spell Power x 10 + 10) damage.

